Enum ECCurve

    public enum ECCurve
extends java.lang.Enum<ECCurve>
    Database of common, public elliptic curves. Data taken from jss.pkcs11.PK11KeyPairGenerator, the OpenJDK CurveDB, and djb's SafeCurves webpage.
